Title: demangle
Description: Converts a symbol that you can get using the addressToSymbol function to the C++ function name.
symbol (String) — Symbol from an object file.
Name of the C++ function, or an empty string if the symbol is not valid. String.
Examples: SELECT    arrayStringConcat(arrayMap(x -> demangle(addressToSymbol(x)), trace), '\n') AS trace_functionsFROM system.trace_logLIMIT 1\G
